| Notes               = * The Curator last appeared as [[Humpty Dumpty]] in ''[[Superboy Vol 1|Superboy (Volume One)]]'' [[Superboy Vol 1 6|#6]]-[[Superboy Vol 1 9|#9]] and [[Superboy Vol 1 11|#11]] in 1950. He was Superboy's first recurring villain.
